/**
 * Support for icons as inline SVG HTMLElements
 */

/* recolor the primary elements of an icon */
.jp-icon0[fill] {
  fill: var(--jp-inverse-layout-color0);
}
.jp-icon1[fill] {
  fill: var(--jp-inverse-layout-color1);
}
.jp-icon2[fill] {
  fill: var(--jp-inverse-layout-color2);
}
.jp-icon3[fill] {
  fill: var(--jp-inverse-layout-color3);
}
.jp-icon4[fill] {
  fill: var(--jp-inverse-layout-color4);
}

.jp-icon0[stroke] {
  stroke: var(--jp-inverse-layout-color0);
}
.jp-icon1[stroke] {
  stroke: var(--jp-inverse-layout-color1);
}
.jp-icon2[stroke] {
  stroke: var(--jp-inverse-layout-color2);
}
.jp-icon3[stroke] {
  stroke: var(--jp-inverse-layout-color3);
}
.jp-icon4[stroke] {
  stroke: var(--jp-inverse-layout-color4);
}
/* recolor the accent elements of an icon */
.jp-icon-accent0[fill] {
  fill: var(--jp-layout-color0);
}
.jp-icon-accent1[fill] {
  fill: var(--jp-layout-color1);
}
.jp-icon-accent2[fill] {

.jp-icon-accent3[fill] {

}

.jp-icon-accent0[stroke] {
  stroke: var(--jp-layout-color0);
}
.jp-icon-accent1[stroke] {
  stroke: var(--jp-layout-color1);
}
.jp-icon-accent2[stroke] {
  stroke: var(--jp-layout-color2);
}
.jp-icon-accent3[stroke] {
  stroke: var(--jp-layout-color3);
}
.jp-icon-accent4[stroke] {
  stroke: var(--jp-layout-color4);
}
/* set the color of an icon to transparent */
.jp-icon-none[fill] {
  fill: none;
}

.jp-icon-none[stroke] {
  stroke: none;
}
/* brand icon colors. Same for light and dark */
.jp-icon-brand0[fill] {
  fill: var(--jp-brand-color0);
}

.jp-icon-brand3[stroke] {
  stroke: var(--jp-brand-color3);
}
.jp-icon-brand4[stroke] {
  stroke: var(--jp-brand-color4);
}
/* warn icon colors. Same for light and dark */

  fill: var(--jp-warn-color0);
}

  fill: var(--jp-warn-color1);

  :hover
  .jp-icon-selectable[fill] {

}

#tab-manager
  .lm-TabBar-tab.jp-mod-active
  .jp-icon-hover
  :hover
  .jp-icon-selectable-inverse[fill] {
  fill: #fff;
}

/**
 * TODO: come up with non css-hack solution for showing the busy icon on top
 *  of the close icon
 * CSS for complex behavior of close icon of tabs in the sidebar tab manager
 */
#tab-manager
  .lm-TabBar-tab.jp-mod-dirty
  > .lm-TabBar-tabCloseIcon
  > :not(:hover)
  > .jp-icon3[fill] {
  fill: none;
}
#tab-manager
  .lm-TabBar-tab.jp-mod-dirty
  > .lm-TabBar-tabCloseIcon
  > :not(:hover)
  > .jp-icon-busy[fill] {
  fill: var(--jp-inverse-layout-color3);
}

#tab-manager
  .lm-TabBar-tab.jp-mod-dirty.jp-mod-active
  > .lm-TabBar-tabCloseIcon
  > :not(:hover)
  > .jp-icon-busy[fill] {
  fill: #fff;
}

/**
* TODO: come up with non css-hack solution for showing the busy icon on top
*  of the close icon
* CSS for complex behavior of close icon of tabs in the main area tabbar
*/
.lm-DockPanel-tabBar
  .lm-TabBar-tab.lm-mod-closable.jp-mod-dirty
  > .lm-TabBar-tabCloseIcon
  > :not(:hover)
  > .jp-icon3[fill] {
  fill: none;
}
.lm-DockPanel-tabBar
  .lm-TabBar-tab.lm-mod-closable.jp-mod-dirty
  > .lm-TabBar-tabCloseIcon
  > :not(:hover)
  > .jp-icon-busy[fill] {
  fill: var(--jp-inverse-layout-color3);
}

/* CSS for icons in status bar */
#jp-main-statusbar .jp-mod-selected .jp-icon-selectable[fill] {
  fill: #fff;
}

#jp-main-statusbar .jp-mod-selected .jp-icon-selectable-inverse[fill] {

.jp-Spinner {
  position: absolute;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  z-index: 10;
  left: 0;
  top: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  background: var(--jp-layout-color0);
  outline: none;
}

.jp-SpinnerContent {
  font-size: 10px;
  margin: 50px auto;
  text-indent: -9999em;
  width: 3em;
  height: 3em;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--jp-brand-color3);
  background: linear-gradient(
    to right,
    #f37626 10%,
    rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) 42%
  );
  position: relative;
  animation: load3 1s infinite linear, fadeIn 1s;
}

.jp-SpinnerContent:before {
  width: 50%;
  height: 50%;
  background: #f37626;
  border-radius: 100% 0 0 0;
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  content: '';
}

.jp-SpinnerContent:after {
  background: var(--jp-layout-color0);
  width: 75%;
  height: 75%;
  border-radius: 50%;
  content: '';
  margin: auto;
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  right: 0;
}

@keyframes fadeIn {
  0% {
    opacity: 0;
  }
  100% {
    opacity: 1;
  }
}

@keyframes load3 {
  0% {
    transform: rotate(0deg);
  }
  100% {
    transform: rotate(360deg);
  }
}

button.jp-mod-styled {
  font-size: var(--jp-ui-font-size1);
  color: var(--jp-ui-font-color0);
  border: none;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  text-align: center;
  line-height: 32px;
  height: 32px;
  padding: 0px 12px;
  letter-spacing: 0.8px;
  outline: none;
  appearance: none;
  -webkit-appearance: none;
  -moz-appearance: none;
}

input.jp-mod-styled {
  background: var(--jp-input-background);
  height: 28px;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  border: var(--jp-border-width) solid var(--jp-border-color1);
  padding-left: 7px;
  padding-right: 7px;
  font-size: var(--jp-ui-font-size2);
  color: var(--jp-ui-font-color0);
  outline: none;
  appearance: none;
  -webkit-appearance: none;
  -moz-appearance: none;
}

input.jp-mod-styled:focus {
  border: var(--jp-border-width) solid var(--md-blue-500);
  box-shadow: inset 0 0 4px var(--md-blue-300);
}

.jp-select-wrapper {
  display: flex;
  position: relative;
  flex-direction: column;
  padding: 1px;
  background-color: var(--jp-layout-color1);
  height: 28px;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}

.jp-select-wrapper.jp-mod-focused select.jp-mod-styled {
  border: var(--jp-border-width) solid var(--jp-input-active-border-color);
  box-shadow: var(--jp-input-box-shadow);
  background-color: var(--jp-input-active-background);
}

select.jp-mod-styled:hover {
  background-color: var(--jp-layout-color1);
  cursor: pointer;
  color: var(--jp-ui-font-color0);
  background-color: var(--jp-input-hover-background);
  box-shadow: inset 0 0px 1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
}

select.jp-mod-styled {
  flex: 1 1 auto;
  height: 32px;
  width: 100%;
  font-size: var(--jp-ui-font-size2);
  background: var(--jp-input-background);
  color: var(--jp-ui-font-color0);
  padding: 0 25px 0 8px;
  border: var(--jp-border-width) solid var(--jp-input-border-color);
  border-radius: 0px;
  outline: none;
  appearance: none;
  -webkit-appearance: none;
  -moz-appearance: none;
}

:root {
  --jp-private-toolbar-height: calc(
    28px + var(--jp-border-width)
  ); /* leave 28px for content */
}

.jp-Toolbar {
  color: var(--jp-ui-font-color1);
  flex: 0 0 auto;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: row;
  border-bottom: var(--jp-border-width) solid var(--jp-toolbar-border-color);
  box-shadow: var(--jp-toolbar-box-shadow);
  background: var(--jp-toolbar-background);
  min-height: var(--jp-toolbar-micro-height);
  padding: 2px;
  z-index: 1;
}

/* Toolbar items */

.jp-Toolbar > .jp-Toolbar-item.jp-Toolbar-spacer {
  flex-grow: 1;
  flex-shrink: 1;
}

.jp-Toolbar-item.jp-Toolbar-kernelStatus {
  display: inline-block;
  width: 32px;
  background-repeat: no-repeat;
  background-position: center;
  background-size: 16px;
}

.jp-Toolbar > .jp-Toolbar-item {
  flex: 0 0 auto;
  display: flex;
  padding-left: 1px;
  padding-right: 1px;
  font-size: var(--jp-ui-font-size1);
  line-height: var(--jp-private-toolbar-height);
  height: 100%;
}

/* Toolbar buttons */

/* This is the div we use to wrap the react component into a Widget */
div.jp-ToolbarButton {
  color: transparent;
  border: none;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  outline: none;
  appearance: none;
  -webkit-appearance: none;
  -moz-appearance: none;
  padding: 0px;
  margin: 0px;
}

button.jp-ToolbarButtonComponent {
  background: var(--jp-layout-color1);
  border: none;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  outline: none;
  appearance: none;
  -webkit-appearance: none;
  -moz-appearance: none;
  padding: 0px 6px;
  margin: 0px;
  height: 24px;
  border-radius: var(--jp-border-radius);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 14px;
  min-width: unset;
  min-height: unset;
}

button.jp-ToolbarButtonComponent:disabled {
  opacity: 0.4;
}

button.jp-ToolbarButtonComponent span {
  padding: 0px;
  flex: 0 0 auto;
}

button.jp-ToolbarButtonComponent .jp-ToolbarButtonComponent-label {
  font-size: var(--jp-ui-font-size1);
  line-height: 100%;
  padding-left: 2px;
  color: var(--jp-ui-font-color1);
}

<h2><br><center><a name="로컬 연결">1. 로컬 연결</a></center></h2>

<div class="jp-Cell-inputWrapper"><div class="jp-InputPrompt jp-InputArea-prompt">
</div><div class="jp-RenderedHTMLCommon jp-RenderedMarkdown jp-MarkdownOutput " data-mime-type="text/markdown">
<p><br>SQLite : 개인용 RDBMS, 모바일기기, 임베디드 시스템, 소규모 웹사이트 운영에 효과적</p>

</div>
</div><div class="jp-Cell jp-CodeCell jp-Notebook-cell   ">
<div class="jp-Cell-inputWrapper">
<div class="jp-InputArea jp-Cell-inputArea">
<div class="jp-InputPrompt jp-InputArea-prompt">In&nbsp;[2]:</div>
<div class="jp-CodeMirrorEditor jp-Editor jp-InputArea-editor" data-type="inline">
     <div class="CodeMirror cm-s-jupyter">
<div class=" highlight hl-ipython3"><pre><span></span><span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">sqlite3</span>   <span class="c1"># sqlite 임포트 하기</span>

<span class="n">conn1</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">sqlite3</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">connect</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;exam.db&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>  <span class="c1"># 현재 모듈과 같은 경로에 db 파일이 저장. 연결 객체가 생성됨</span>
<span class="n">conn2</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">sqlite3</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">connect</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;:memory:&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>  <span class="c1"># RAM에 db가 저장 : 휘발성. 연결 객체가 생성됨</span>


<span class="k">try</span><span class="p">:</span>
    <span class="n">cur</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">conn2</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">cursor</span><span class="p">()</span>  <span class="c1"># SQL을 실행 가능 객체</span>
    
    <span class="c1"># 자료 입력</span>
    <span class="n">cur</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">execute</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;create table if not exists friends(name text, phone text, addr text)&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>  
    <span class="n">cur</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">execute</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;insert into friends values(&#39;홍길동&#39;,&#39;111-1111&#39;,&#39;역삼1동&#39;)&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">cur</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">execute</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;insert into friends values(&#39;고길동&#39;,&#39;222-1111&#39;,&#39;서초1동&#39;)&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>
    
    <span class="n">inputData</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;손오공&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s1">&#39;333-1111&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s1">&#39;압구정동&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">cur</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">execute</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;insert into friends values(?,?,?)&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">inputData</span><span class="p">)</span>  <span class="c1"># 이런방식으로도 넣을 수 있다.</span>
    
    <span class="n">conn2</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">commit</span><span class="p">()</span>
    
    <span class="c1"># 자료 읽기</span>
    <span class="n">cur</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">execute</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;select * from friends&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">cur</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">fetchone</span><span class="p">())</span>  <span class="c1"># 레코드 포인터가 있는 지점의 레코드를 참조, 튜플형식으로 출력</span>
    <span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">cur</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">fetchone</span><span class="p">())</span>
    
    <span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">cur</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">fetchall</span><span class="p">())</span>  <span class="c1"># 레코드 포인터 위치부터 전체 레코드 출력, 튜플을 리스트로 묶어서 출력</span>
    
    <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">r</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">cur</span><span class="p">:</span>
        <span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">r</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="s1">&#39; &#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">r</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="s1">&#39; &#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">r</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">])</span>  <span class="c1"># 원하는 방법으로 출력</span>
     
    
<span class="k">except</span> <span class="ne">Exception</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="n">e</span><span class="p">:</span>
    <span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;err : &#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">e</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">conn2</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">rollback</span><span class="p">()</span>
    
    
<span class="k">finally</span><span class="p">:</span>
    <span class="n">conn2</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">close</span><span class="p">()</span>
</pre></div>

<div class=" highlight hl-ipython3"><pre><span></span><span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">dbFunc</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">dbName</span><span class="p">):</span>
    <span class="k">try</span><span class="p">:</span>
        <span class="n">conn</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">sqlite3</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">connect</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">dbName</span><span class="p">)</span>
        <span class="n">cur</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">conn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">cursor</span><span class="p">()</span>
        
        <span class="c1"># 테이블 생성</span>
        <span class="n">cur</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">execute</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;drop table if exists jiktab&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>
        <span class="n">cur</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">execute</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;create table jiktab(id integer primary key, name text)&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>
        
        <span class="c1"># insert (튜플, 리스트 가능)</span>
        <span class="n">cur</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">execute</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;insert into jiktab values(1,&#39;홍길동&#39;)&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>
        
        <span class="n">tdata</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="s1">&#39;고길동&#39;</span>  <span class="c1"># 튜플타입</span>
        <span class="n">cur</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">execute</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;insert into jiktab values(?,?)&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">tdata</span><span class="p">)</span>
        
        <span class="n">ldata</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="s1">&#39;김밥&#39;</span><span class="p">]</span>  <span class="c1"># 리스트타입</span>
        <span class="n">cur</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">execute</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;insert into jiktab values(?,?)&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">ldata</span><span class="p">)</span>
        
        <span class="n">ddata</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">{</span><span class="s1">&#39;id&#39;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s1">&#39;name&#39;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="s1">&#39;공기밥&#39;</span><span class="p">}</span>
        <span class="n">cur</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">execute</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;insert into jiktab values(:id,:name)&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">ddata</span><span class="p">)</span>  <span class="c1"># 딕셔너리 타입, 물음표를 쓰면 안됨</span>
        
        <span class="n">conn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">commit</span><span class="p">()</span>
        
        <span class="c1"># update</span>
        <span class="n">updata</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;박치기&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">)</span>
        <span class="n">cur</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">execute</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;update jiktab set name=? where id=?&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">updata</span><span class="p">)</span>
        
        <span class="c1"># delete</span>
        <span class="n">deldata</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,)</span>
        <span class="n">cur</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">execute</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;delete from jiktab where id=?&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">deldata</span><span class="p">)</span>
        
        <span class="n">conn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">commit</span><span class="p">()</span>
        
        <span class="c1"># select</span>
        <span class="n">cur</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">execute</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;select * from jiktab&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>
        <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">r</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">cur</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">r</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">])</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="s2">&quot; &quot;</span><span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">r</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">])</span>
        
        <span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">()</span>
        <span class="n">cur</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">execute</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;select * from jiktab where id &lt;= 2&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>
        <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">r</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">cur</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">r</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">])</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="s1">&#39; &#39;</span><span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">r</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">])</span>
            
        <span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">()</span>
        <span class="n">cur</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">execute</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;select * from jiktab&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>
        <span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;건수 : &#39;</span><span class="o">+</span> <span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">cur</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">fetchone</span><span class="p">()[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]))</span>
        
        <span class="n">conn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">commit</span><span class="p">()</span>
        
        
    <span class="k">except</span> <span class="ne">Exception</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="n">e</span><span class="p">:</span>
        <span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;err : &#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">e</span><span class="p">)</span>
        <span class="n">conn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">rollback</span><span class="p">()</span>
        
        
    <span class="k">finally</span><span class="p">:</span>
        <span class="k">pass</span>
    
    
<span class="k">if</span> <span class="vm">__name__</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="s1">&#39;__main__&#39;</span><span class="p">:</span>
    <span class="n">dbFunc</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;test.db&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>
</pre></div>

    <span class="n">sql</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s2">&quot;insert into sangdata(code,sang,su,dan) values(5,&#39;상품1&#39;,7,1000)&quot;</span>

    <span class="n">sql</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s2">&quot;insert into sangdata(code,sang,su,dan) values(</span><span class="si">%s</span><span class="s2">,</span><span class="si">%s</span><span class="s2">,</span><span class="si">%s</span><span class="s2">,</span><span class="si">%s</span><span class="s2">)&quot;</span>
    <span class="n">cursor</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">execute</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">sql</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">ins_data</span><span class="p">)</span>  <span class="c1"># 파이썬에만 데이터가 들어와있음 </span>

    <span class="n">up_data</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;파이썬&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">33</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">10</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">cursor</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">execute</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">sql</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">up_data</span><span class="p">)</span>
    
    <span class="n">conn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">commit</span><span class="p">()</span>
    
    <span class="c1"># 자료 삭제</span>

    <span class="n">cursor</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">execute</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">sql</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">del_data</span><span class="p">)</span>

    <span class="n">conn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">commit</span><span class="p">()</span>
    
    <span class="c1"># 자료 읽기</span>
    <span class="n">sql</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s2">&quot;select code,sang,su,dan from sangdata&quot;</span>

    <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">data</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">cursor</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">fetchall</span><span class="p">():</span>
        <span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="p">)</span>
    
    <span class="sd">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span>
<span class="sd">    # 다른 읽기 방법1</span>

<span class="sd">  </span>
<span class="sd">    # 다른 읽기 방법2</span>

<span class="sd">    &quot;&quot;&quot;</span>
    
<span class="k">except</span> <span class="ne">Exception</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="n">e</span><span class="p">:</span>

<span class="k">finally</span><span class="p">:</span>
    <span class="n">conn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">close</span><span class="p">()</span>
</pre></div>

        <span class="c1"># lstGogek 객체에 제목달기 (직접 추가 해줘야 함)</span>
        <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">lstGogek</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">InsertColumn</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s1">&#39;고객번호&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">width</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">100</span><span class="p">)</span>
        <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">lstGogek</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">InsertColumn</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s1">&#39;고객명&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">width</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">150</span><span class="p">)</span>
        <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">lstGogek</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">InsertColumn</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s1">&#39;고객전화&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">width</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">200</span><span class="p">)</span>
        
        <span class="c1"># Connect Events</span>
        <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">btnLogin</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Bind</span><span class="p">(</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">EVT_BUTTON</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">OnLogin</span> <span class="p">)</span>
    
    <span class="k">def</span> <span class="fm">__del__</span><span class="p">(</span> <span class="bp">self</span> <span class="p">):</span>
        <span class="k">pass</span>
    
    
    <span class="c1"># Virtual event handlers, overide them in your derived class</span>
    <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">OnLogin</span><span class="p">(</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">event</span> <span class="p">):</span>
        <span class="k">if</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">txtNo</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">GetValue</span><span class="p">()</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="s1">&#39;&#39;</span><span class="p">:</span>  <span class="c1"># 사번 입력 검사</span>
            <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">MessageBox</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;사번을 입력하시오&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s1">&#39;알림&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">OK</span><span class="p">)</span>
            <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">txtNo</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetFocus</span><span class="p">()</span>  <span class="c1"># 커서 깜빡이게 한다</span>
            <span class="k">return</span>
        
        <span class="k">if</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">txtName</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">GetValue</span><span class="p">()</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="s1">&#39;&#39;</span><span class="p">:</span>  <span class="c1"># 직원명 검사</span>
            <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">MessageBox</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;직원을 입력하시오&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s1">&#39;알림&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">OK</span><span class="p">)</span>
            <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">txtName</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetFocus</span><span class="p">()</span>
            <span class="k">return</span>
        
        <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">LoginCheck</span><span class="p">()</span>  <span class="c1"># 입력자료가 만족되는 로그인 처리 메소드를 호출</span>
        
    <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">LoginCheck</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">):</span>  <span class="c1"># DB와 연동을 하는 시점</span>
        <span class="k">try</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="n">conn</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">MySQLdb</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">connect</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">**</span><span class="n">config</span><span class="p">)</span> 
            <span class="n">cursor</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">conn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">cursor</span><span class="p">()</span>
            <span class="n">no</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">txtNo</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">GetValue</span><span class="p">()</span>
            <span class="n">name</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">txtName</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">GetValue</span><span class="p">()</span>
            
            <span class="n">sql</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s2">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span>
<span class="s2">            select count(jikwon_no) from jikwon</span>
<span class="s2">            where jikwon_no=</span><span class="si">{0}</span><span class="s2"> and jikwon_name=&#39;</span><span class="si">{1}</span><span class="s2">&#39;</span>
<span class="s2">            &quot;&quot;&quot;</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">format</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">no</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">name</span><span class="p">)</span>
            
            <span class="n">cursor</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">execute</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">sql</span><span class="p">)</span>
            <span class="n">count</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">cursor</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">fetchone</span><span class="p">()[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span>  <span class="c1"># 정보가 맞으면 1, 틀리면 0</span>
            <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">count</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">:</span>
                <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">MessageBox</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;로그인 실패&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s1">&#39;알림&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">OK</span><span class="p">)</span>
                <span class="k">return</span>
            
            <span class="k">else</span><span class="p">:</span>
                <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">staMsg</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetLabelText</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">no</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="s1">&#39;번 직원의 관리고객 목록&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>
                <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">DisplayData</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">no</span><span class="p">)</span>
                
        <span class="k">except</span> <span class="ne">Exception</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="n">e</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">MessageBox</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;로그인 체크 에러:&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">e</span><span class="p">))</span>
        
        <span class="k">finally</span><span class="p">:</span>  <span class="c1"># 끝나면 꼭 닫아준다</span>
            <span class="n">cursor</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">close</span><span class="p">()</span>
            <span class="n">conn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">close</span><span class="p">()</span>
        
    <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">DisplayData</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">no</span><span class="p">):</span>
        <span class="k">try</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="n">conn</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">MySQLdb</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">connect</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">**</span><span class="n">config</span><span class="p">)</span>
            <span class="n">cursor</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">conn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">cursor</span><span class="p">()</span>
            <span class="n">sql</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s2">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span>
<span class="s2">            select gogek_no,gogek_name,gogek_tel from gogek where gogek_damsano=</span><span class="si">{}</span><span class="s2"></span>
<span class="s2">            &quot;&quot;&quot;</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">format</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">no</span><span class="p">)</span>
                
            <span class="n">cursor</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">execute</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">sql</span><span class="p">)</span>
            <span class="n">gogekDatas</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">cursor</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">fetchall</span><span class="p">()</span>
                
            <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">lstGogek</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">DeleteAllItems</span><span class="p">()</span>  <span class="c1"># 고객목록 창 초기화</span>
            <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">gdata</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">gogekDatas</span><span class="p">:</span>
                <span class="n">i</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">lstGogek</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">InsertItem</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">1000</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">)</span>    <span class="c1"># 최대 행수를 적어준다</span>
                <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">lstGogek</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetItem</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">gdata</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]))</span>    <span class="c1"># i행 0열</span>
                <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">lstGogek</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetItem</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">gdata</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">])</span>
                <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">lstGogek</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetItem</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">gdata</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">])</span>
            <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">staCount</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetLabelText</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;인원 수 : &#39;</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">gogekDatas</span><span class="p">)))</span>
                
        <span class="k">except</span> <span class="ne">Exception</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="n">e</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">MessageBox</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;고객 출력 에러 : &#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">e</span><span class="p">))</span>
                
        <span class="k">finally</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="n">cursor</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">close</span><span class="p">()</span>
            <span class="n">conn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">close</span><span class="p">()</span>
        
<span class="k">if</span> <span class="vm">__name__</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="s1">&#39;__main__&#39;</span><span class="p">:</span>
    <span class="n">app</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">App</span><span class="p">()</span>
    <span class="n">MyFrameLogin</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kc">None</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Show</span><span class="p">()</span>
    <span class="n">app</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">MainLoop</span><span class="p">()</span>
</pre></div>

<div class=" highlight hl-ipython3"><pre><span></span><span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">wx</span>
<span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">wx.xrc</span>
<span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">MySQLdb</span>

<span class="n">config</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">{</span>
    <span class="s1">&#39;host&#39;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="s1">&#39;127.0.0.1&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span>
    <span class="s1">&#39;user&#39;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="s1">&#39;root&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span>
    <span class="s1">&#39;password&#39;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="s1">&#39;123&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span>
    <span class="s1">&#39;database&#39;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="s1">&#39;test&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span>

<span class="p">}</span>

<span class="k">class</span> <span class="nc">JikwonInfo</span><span class="p">(</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Frame</span> <span class="p">):</span>
    
    <span class="k">def</span> <span class="fm">__init__</span><span class="p">(</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">parent</span> <span class="p">):</span>
        <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Frame</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="fm">__init__</span> <span class="p">(</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">parent</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nb">id</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">ID_ANY</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">title</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">EmptyString</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">pos</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">DefaultPosition</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">size</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Size</span><span class="p">(</span> <span class="mi">400</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">300</span> <span class="p">),</span> <span class="n">style</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">DEFAULT_FRAME_STYLE</span><span class="o">|</span><span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">TAB_TRAVERSAL</span> <span class="p">)</span>
        
        <span class="c1"># self.SetSizeHintsSz( wx.DefaultSize, wx.DefaultSize )</span>
        <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetBackgroundColour</span><span class="p">(</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SystemSettings</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">GetColour</span><span class="p">(</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SYS_COLOUR_MENU</span> <span class="p">)</span> <span class="p">)</span>
        
        <span class="n">bSizer1</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">BoxSizer</span><span class="p">(</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">VERTICAL</span> <span class="p">)</span>
        
        <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">m_panel1</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Panel</span><span class="p">(</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">ID_ANY</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">DefaultPosition</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">DefaultSize</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">TAB_TRAVERSAL</span> <span class="p">)</span>
        <span class="n">bSizer3</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">BoxSizer</span><span class="p">(</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">HORIZONTAL</span> <span class="p">)</span>
        
        <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">m_staticText1</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">StaticText</span><span class="p">(</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">m_panel1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">ID_ANY</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="sa">u</span><span class="s2">&quot;직급입력 : &quot;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">DefaultPosition</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">DefaultSize</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">0</span> <span class="p">)</span>

    <span class="c1"># 구조 설명</span>
    <span class="sd">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span>
<span class="sd">    OnSearch 에서는 입력 여부를 판단한다. 아무것도 입력이 안되있으면 전체직원정보 출력, 입력되있으면 SearchCheck으로 넘긴다</span>
<span class="sd">    SearchCheck 에서는 입력한 직급이 있는직급인지 없는직급인지 판단한다. 없으면 창 출력, 있으면 DisplayData로 넘긴다</span>
<span class="sd">    DisplayData 에서는 깔끔하게 출력하면 끝 ~~~~</span>
<span class="sd">    &quot;&quot;&quot;</span>

    <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">OnSearch</span><span class="p">(</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">event</span> <span class="p">):</span>
        
        <span class="c1"># 직급 입력안했을시 전체 정보 출력</span>
        <span class="k">if</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">txtJik</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">GetValue</span><span class="p">()</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="s1">&#39;&#39;</span><span class="p">:</span>  
            <span class="n">conn</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">MySQLdb</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">connect</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">**</span><span class="n">config</span><span class="p">)</span> 
            <span class="n">cursor</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">conn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">cursor</span><span class="p">()</span>

            <span class="c1"># 평균연봉도 구하기 위해 jikwon_pay 까지 일단 받아둔다</span>
            <span class="n">sql</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s2">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span>
<span class="s2">            select jikwon_no,jikwon_name,buser_name,jikwon_gen,jikwon_pay from jikwon </span>
<span class="s2">            left outer join buser on buser_num=buser_no</span>
<span class="s2">            &quot;&quot;&quot;</span>
            <span class="n">cursor</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">execute</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">sql</span><span class="p">)</span>   
            
            <span class="n">jikDatas</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">cursor</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">fetchall</span><span class="p">()</span>

            <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">lstJikwon</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">DeleteAllItems</span><span class="p">()</span>  <span class="c1"># 직원목록 창 초기화</span>
            
            <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">jdata</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">jikDatas</span><span class="p">:</span>
                <span class="n">i</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">lstJikwon</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">InsertItem</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">1000</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">)</span>    <span class="c1"># 최대 행수를 적어준다</span>
                <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">lstJikwon</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetItem</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">jdata</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]))</span>  <span class="c1"># i행 0열</span>
                <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">lstJikwon</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetItem</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">jdata</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">])</span>
                <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">lstJikwon</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetItem</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">jdata</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">])</span>
                <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">lstJikwon</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetItem</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">jdata</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">])</span>
            
            <span class="c1"># 인원 수 출력</span>
            <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">staCount</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetLabelText</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">jikDatas</span><span class="p">)))</span>
                
            <span class="c1"># 평균 연봉 계산 후 출력</span>
            <span class="n">pay</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">0</span>
            <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">i</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">jikDatas</span><span class="p">:</span>
                <span class="n">pay</span> <span class="o">+=</span> <span class="n">i</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">]</span>
            <span class="n">payavg</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">round</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">pay</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">jikDatas</span><span class="p">))</span>
            <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">staPayavg</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetLabelText</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">payavg</span><span class="p">))</span>        
            <span class="k">return</span>  <span class="c1"># 함수 끝낸다</span>
            
        <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SearchCheck</span><span class="p">()</span>  <span class="c1"># 무언가가 입력되있고 검색을 눌렀을때 실행</span>
    
    
    <span class="c1"># 직급이 있는 직급인지 없는 직급인지 확인후, 없으면 알림을 띄운다, 있으면 display 한다</span>
    <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">SearchCheck</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">):</span>
        <span class="k">try</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="n">conn</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">MySQLdb</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">connect</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">**</span><span class="n">config</span><span class="p">)</span> 
            <span class="n">cursor</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">conn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">cursor</span><span class="p">()</span>
            
            <span class="n">jik</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">txtJik</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">GetValue</span><span class="p">()</span>

            <span class="n">sql</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s2">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span>
<span class="s2">            select count(jikwon_jik) from jikwon</span>
<span class="s2">            where jikwon_jik=&#39;</span><span class="si">{}</span><span class="s2">&#39;</span>
<span class="s2">            &quot;&quot;&quot;</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">format</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">jik</span><span class="p">)</span>

            <span class="n">cursor</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">execute</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">sql</span><span class="p">)</span>
            <span class="n">count</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">cursor</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">fetchone</span><span class="p">()[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span>  <span class="c1"># 직급이 없으면 0 반환</span>
            <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">count</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">:</span>
                <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">MessageBox</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;없는 직급 입니다&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s1">&#39;알림&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">OK</span><span class="p">)</span>
                
            <span class="k">else</span><span class="p">:</span>
                <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">DisplayData</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">jik</span><span class="p">)</span>
        
        <span class="k">except</span> <span class="ne">Exception</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="n">e</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">MessageBox</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;검색 에러&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>
            
        <span class="k">finally</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="n">cursor</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">close</span><span class="p">()</span>
            <span class="n">conn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">close</span><span class="p">()</span>
    
    
    <span class="c1"># 깔끔하게 출력</span>
    <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">DisplayData</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">jik</span><span class="p">):</span>
        <span class="k">try</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="n">conn</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">MySQLdb</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">connect</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">**</span><span class="n">config</span><span class="p">)</span> 
            <span class="n">cursor</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">conn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">cursor</span><span class="p">()</span>
            
            <span class="c1"># 나중에 평균연봉도 구하기 위해 jikwon_pay 까지 일단 받아둔다</span>
            <span class="n">sql</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s2">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span>
<span class="s2">            select jikwon_no,jikwon_name,buser_name,jikwon_gen,jikwon_pay from jikwon </span>
<span class="s2">            left outer join buser on buser_num=buser_no where jikwon_jik=&#39;</span><span class="si">{}</span><span class="s2">&#39;</span>
<span class="s2">            &quot;&quot;&quot;</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">format</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">jik</span><span class="p">)</span>
            <span class="n">cursor</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">execute</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">sql</span><span class="p">)</span>

            <span class="n">jikDatas</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">cursor</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">fetchall</span><span class="p">()</span>

            <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">lstJikwon</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">DeleteAllItems</span><span class="p">()</span>  <span class="c1"># 직원목록 창 초기화</span>
            
            <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">jdata</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">jikDatas</span><span class="p">:</span>
                <span class="n">i</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">lstJikwon</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">InsertItem</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">1000</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">)</span>    <span class="c1"># 최대 행수를 적어준다</span>
                <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">lstJikwon</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetItem</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">jdata</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]))</span>  <span class="c1"># i행 0열</span>
                <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">lstJikwon</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetItem</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">jdata</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">])</span>
                <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">lstJikwon</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetItem</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">jdata</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">])</span>
                <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">lstJikwon</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetItem</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">jdata</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">])</span>
            
            <span class="c1"># 인원 수 출력</span>
            <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">staCount</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetLabelText</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">jikDatas</span><span class="p">)))</span>
                
            <span class="c1"># 평균 연봉 계산 후 출력</span>
            <span class="n">pay</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">0</span>
            <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">i</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">jikDatas</span><span class="p">:</span>
                <span class="n">pay</span> <span class="o">+=</span> <span class="n">i</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">]</span>
            <span class="n">payavg</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">round</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">pay</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">jikDatas</span><span class="p">))</span>
            <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">staPayavg</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetLabelText</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">payavg</span><span class="p">))</span>
            
        <span class="k">except</span> <span class="ne">Exception</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="n">e</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">MessageBox</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;직원 출력 에러&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>
        
        <span class="k">finally</span><span class="p">:</span>  <span class="c1"># 끝나면 꼭 닫아준다</span>
            <span class="n">cursor</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">close</span><span class="p">()</span>
            <span class="n">conn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">close</span><span class="p">()</span>
    
    <span class="c1"># 종료 메소드</span>
    <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">Exit</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">event</span><span class="p">):</span>
        <span class="n">dlg</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">MessageDialog</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s1">&#39;정말 종료할까요?&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s1">&#39;알림&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">YES_NO</span><span class="p">)</span>   
        <span class="n">imsi</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">dlg</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">ShowModal</span><span class="p">()</span>
        <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">imsi</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">ID_YES</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="n">dlg</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Destroy</span><span class="p">()</span>    <span class="c1"># 대화 상자 닫기</span>
            <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Close</span><span class="p">()</span>    <span class="c1"># Frame 닫기</span>
        
        
<span class="k">if</span> <span class="vm">__name__</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="s1">&#39;__main__&#39;</span><span class="p">:</span>
    <span class="n">app</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">App</span><span class="p">()</span>
    <span class="n">JikwonInfo</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kc">None</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Show</span><span class="p">()</span>
    <span class="n">app</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">MainLoop</span><span class="p">()</span>
</pre></div>

<div class="jp-CodeMirrorEditor jp-Editor jp-InputArea-editor" data-type="inline">
     <div class="CodeMirror cm-s-jupyter">
<div class=" highlight hl-ipython3"><pre><span></span><span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">wx</span>
<span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">wx.xrc</span>
<span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">ast</span>  <span class="c1"># sting 파일을 dict로 읽는다</span>
<span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">MySQLdb</span>


<span class="c1"># 주소 파일 읽어오기</span>
<span class="k">with</span> <span class="nb">open</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;mariadb.txt&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s1">&#39;r&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="n">f</span><span class="p">:</span>
    <span class="n">config</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">ast</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">literal_eval</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">f</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">read</span><span class="p">())</span>
    
<span class="n">datas</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[]</span>
<span class="n">rec_r</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">0</span>  <span class="c1"># 레코드 번호</span>

            <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">rec_r</span> <span class="o">&gt;</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">datas</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">):</span><span class="n">rec_r</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">datas</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="mi">1</span>
        <span class="k">elif</span> <span class="nb">id</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">:</span>  <span class="c1"># &gt;&gt;&gt; 버튼은 마지막 값 보여준다</span>
            <span class="n">rec_r</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">datas</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="mi">1</span>
        
        <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">ShowData</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">rec_r</span><span class="p">)</span>
    
    <span class="c1"># db 연결</span>
    <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">DbLoad</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">):</span>
        <span class="k">try</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="n">conn</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">MySQLdb</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">connect</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">**</span><span class="n">config</span><span class="p">)</span>
            <span class="n">cursor</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">conn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">cursor</span><span class="p">()</span>
            <span class="n">sql</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s2">&quot;select * from jikwon&quot;</span>
            <span class="n">cursor</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">execute</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">sql</span><span class="p">)</span>
            <span class="k">global</span> <span class="n">datas</span>
            <span class="n">datas</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">cursor</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">fetchall</span><span class="p">()</span>
           
            <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">ShowData</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">rec_r</span><span class="p">)</span>
            
        <span class="k">except</span> <span class="ne">Exception</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="n">e</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">MessageBox</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;연결 에러&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s1">&#39;에러&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">OK</span><span class="p">)</span>
            
        <span class="k">finally</span><span class="p">:</span> 
            <span class="n">cursor</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">close</span><span class="p">()</span>
            <span class="n">conn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">close</span><span class="p">()</span>
        
    <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">ShowData</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">r</span><span class="p">):</span>
        <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">txtNo</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetLabel</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">datas</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">r</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]))</span>
        <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">txtName</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetLabel</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">datas</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">r</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">]))</span>
    
    
<span class="k">if</span> <span class="vm">__name__</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="s1">&#39;__main__&#39;</span><span class="p">:</span>
    <span class="n">app</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">App</span><span class="p">()</span>
    <span class="n">MyFrame1</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kc">None</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Show</span><span class="p">()</span>
    <span class="n">app</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">MainLoop</span><span class="p">()</span>
</pre></div>

        <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">btnConfirm</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Enable</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">enable</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="kc">False</span><span class="p">)</span>  <span class="c1"># 수정 확인 버튼은 비활성화 상태에서 출발</span>

    <span class="k">def</span> <span class="fm">__del__</span><span class="p">(</span> <span class="bp">self</span> <span class="p">):</span>
        <span class="k">pass</span>
    
    <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">BtnProcess</span><span class="p">(</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">event</span> <span class="p">):</span>
        <span class="nb">id</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">event</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">GetEventObject</span><span class="p">()</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">id</span>
        
        <span class="k">if</span> <span class="nb">id</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">MemInsert</span><span class="p">()</span>  <span class="c1"># 등록처리 메소드 호출</span>
            
        <span class="k">elif</span> <span class="nb">id</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">MemUpdateReady</span><span class="p">()</span>  <span class="c1"># 수정준비 메소드 호출</span>
            
        <span class="k">elif</span> <span class="nb">id</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">MemUpdateProcess</span><span class="p">()</span>  <span class="c1"># 수정처리 메소드 호출</span>
            
        <span class="k">elif</span> <span class="nb">id</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">:</span>
