            <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">MemUpdateCancel</span><span class="p">()</span>  <span class="c1"># 수정취소 메소드 호출           </span>
            
    <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">ShowData</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">):</span>
        <span class="k">try</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="n">conn</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">MySQLdb</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">connect</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">**</span><span class="n">config</span><span class="p">)</span>
            <span class="n">cursor</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">conn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">cursor</span><span class="p">()</span>
            
            <span class="n">sql</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s2">&quot;select * from pymem&quot;</span>
            <span class="n">cursor</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">execute</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">sql</span><span class="p">)</span>
            
            <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">lstMember</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">DeleteAllItems</span><span class="p">()</span>  <span class="c1"># 초기화</span>
            <span class="n">count</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">0</span>
            <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">data</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">cursor</span><span class="p">:</span>
                <span class="n">i</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">lstMember</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">InsertItem</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">10000</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">)</span>  <span class="c1"># 동적인 번호 부여</span>
                <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">lstMember</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetItem</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]))</span>  <span class="c1"># 번호</span>
                <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">lstMember</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetItem</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">])</span>  <span class="c1"># 이름</span>
                <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">lstMember</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetItem</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">])</span>  <span class="c1"># 전화</span>
                <span class="n">count</span> <span class="o">+=</span> <span class="mi">1</span>
                
            <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">lblCnt</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetLabel</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">count</span><span class="p">))</span>
            
        <span class="k">except</span> <span class="ne">Exception</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="n">e</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">MessageBox</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;읽기 오류 : &#39;</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">e</span><span class="p">),</span> <span class="s1">&#39;에러&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">OK</span><span class="p">)</span>
        
        <span class="k">finally</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="n">cursor</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">close</span><span class="p">()</span>
            <span class="n">conn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">close</span><span class="p">()</span>
 
    <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">MemInsert</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">):</span>  <span class="c1"># 회원추가</span>
        <span class="n">no</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">txtNo</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">GetValue</span><span class="p">()</span>
        <span class="n">name</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">txtName</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">GetValue</span><span class="p">()</span>
        <span class="n">tel</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">txtTel</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">GetValue</span><span class="p">()</span>
        
        <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">no</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="s1">&#39;&#39;</span> <span class="ow">or</span> <span class="n">name</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="s1">&#39;&#39;</span> <span class="ow">or</span> <span class="n">tel</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="s1">&#39;&#39;</span><span class="p">:</span>  <span class="c1"># 값을 입력 안했을 때</span>
            <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">MessageBox</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;자료를 입력하시오&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s1">&#39;알림&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">OK</span><span class="p">)</span>
            <span class="k">return</span>
        
        <span class="k">try</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="n">conn</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">MySQLdb</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">connect</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">**</span><span class="n">config</span><span class="p">)</span>
            <span class="n">cursor</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">conn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">cursor</span><span class="p">()</span>
            
            <span class="c1"># 새로운 번호의 등록이 가능한지 확인 작업 </span>
            <span class="n">data</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SelectData</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">no</span><span class="p">)</span>
            <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">data</span> <span class="o">!=</span> <span class="kc">None</span><span class="p">:</span>
                <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">MessageBox</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;이미 등록된 번호입니다&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s1">&#39;알림&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">OK</span><span class="p">)</span>
                <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">txtNo</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetFocus</span><span class="p">()</span>  <span class="c1"># 맨위로 커서를 올림</span>
                <span class="k">return</span>
            
            <span class="c1"># 등록이 가능한 상태라면 등록작업 계속 진행</span>
            <span class="n">sql</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s2">&quot;insert into pymem values(</span><span class="si">%s</span><span class="s2">,</span><span class="si">%s</span><span class="s2">,</span><span class="si">%s</span><span class="s2">)&quot;</span>
            <span class="n">cursor</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">execute</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">sql</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">no</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">name</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">tel</span><span class="p">))</span>
            <span class="n">conn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">commit</span><span class="p">()</span>  <span class="c1"># commit을 해야 데이터 베이스에 등록이 됨</span>
            <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">ShowData</span><span class="p">()</span>  <span class="c1"># 결과 띄우기</span>
            
            <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">txtNo</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetValue</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>  <span class="c1"># 화면에 입력한 자료 초기화</span>
            <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">txtName</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetValue</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>
            <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">txtTel</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetValue</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>
            
        <span class="k">except</span> <span class="ne">Exception</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="n">e</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">MessageBox</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;추가 오류 : &#39;</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">e</span><span class="p">),</span> <span class="s1">&#39;에러&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">OK</span> <span class="p">)</span>
            <span class="n">conn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">rollback</span><span class="p">()</span>
        
        <span class="k">finally</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="n">cursor</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">close</span><span class="p">()</span>
            <span class="n">conn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">close</span><span class="p">()</span>
        
    <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">MemUpdateReady</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">):</span>  <span class="c1"># 회원수정 준비</span>
        <span class="n">textDlg</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">TextEntryDialog</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kc">None</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s1">&#39;수정할 번호를 입력하시오&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s1">&#39;알림&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>  <span class="c1"># 입력창 띄우기</span>
        <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">textDlg</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">ShowModal</span><span class="p">()</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">ID_OK</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">textDlg</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">GetValue</span><span class="p">()</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="s1">&#39;&#39;</span><span class="p">:</span>
                <span class="k">return</span>
            <span class="n">upno</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">textDlg</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">GetValue</span><span class="p">()</span>
            <span class="n">data</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SelectData</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">upno</span><span class="p">)</span>
            <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">data</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="kc">None</span><span class="p">:</span>
                <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">MessageBox</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">upno</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="s2">&quot;번은 등록된자료가 아닙니다&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>
                <span class="k">return</span>
            
            <span class="c1"># 수정 준비작업 계속</span>
            <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">txtNo</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetValue</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]))</span>  <span class="c1"># 수정할 자료 화면에 표시</span>
            <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">txtName</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetValue</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">])</span>
            <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">txtTel</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetValue</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">])</span>
            
            <span class="c1"># 번호칸 비활성화</span>
            <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">txtNo</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetEditable</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kc">False</span><span class="p">)</span>  
            
            <span class="c1"># 수정에서 취소로 변경</span>
            <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">btnUpdate</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetLabel</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;취소&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>  
            <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">btnUpdate</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">id</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">5</span> 
            
            <span class="c1"># 확인버튼 활성화</span>
            <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">btnConfirm</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Enable</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">enable</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="kc">True</span><span class="p">)</span>
            
        <span class="k">else</span><span class="p">:</span>  <span class="c1"># 취소 눌렀을 때 </span>
            <span class="k">return</span>
        <span class="n">textDlg</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Destroy</span><span class="p">()</span>  <span class="c1"># TextEntryDialog 닫기 마무리 처리함</span>
            
    <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">MemUpdateProcess</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">):</span>  <span class="c1"># 회원수정 처리</span>
        <span class="n">no</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">txtNo</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">GetValue</span><span class="p">()</span>
        <span class="n">name</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">txtName</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">GetValue</span><span class="p">()</span>
        <span class="n">tel</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">txtTel</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">GetValue</span><span class="p">()</span>
        
        <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">name</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="s1">&#39;&#39;</span> <span class="ow">or</span> <span class="n">tel</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="s1">&#39;&#39;</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">MessageBox</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;수정 자료를 입력하시오&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s1">&#39;알림&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">OK</span><span class="p">)</span>
            <span class="k">return</span>
        
        <span class="k">try</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="n">conn</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">MySQLdb</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">connect</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">**</span><span class="n">config</span><span class="p">)</span>
            <span class="n">cursor</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">conn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">cursor</span><span class="p">()</span>
            
            <span class="n">sql</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s2">&quot;update pymem set irum=</span><span class="si">%s</span><span class="s2">, junhwa=</span><span class="si">%s</span><span class="s2"> where bun=</span><span class="si">%s</span><span class="s2">&quot;</span>
            <span class="n">cursor</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">execute</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">sql</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">name</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">tel</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">no</span><span class="p">))</span>
            <span class="n">conn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">commit</span><span class="p">()</span>
            <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">ShowData</span><span class="p">()</span>
            <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">MemUpdateCancel</span><span class="p">()</span>  <span class="c1"># 수정 후 화면 초기화</span>
            
        <span class="k">except</span> <span class="ne">Exception</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="n">e</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">MessageBox</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;수정 에러 : &#39;</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">e</span><span class="p">),</span> <span class="s1">&#39;알림&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">OK</span><span class="p">)</span>
            <span class="n">conn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">rollback</span><span class="p">()</span>
            
        <span class="k">finally</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="n">cursor</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">close</span><span class="p">()</span>
            <span class="n">conn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">close</span><span class="p">()</span>
    
    <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">MemUpdateCancel</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">):</span>  <span class="c1"># 회원수정 준비를 취소</span>
        <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">txtNo</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetValue</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>
        <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">txtName</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetValue</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>
        <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">txtTel</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetValue</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>
        
        <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">txtNo</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetEditable</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kc">True</span><span class="p">)</span>  <span class="c1"># 이름칸 다시 작성 가능</span>
        <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">btnUpdate</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetLabel</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;수정&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>
        <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">btnUpdate</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">id</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">2</span>
        <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">btnConfirm</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Enable</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">enable</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="kc">False</span><span class="p">)</span>  <span class="c1"># 확인칸 다시 비활성화</span>
    
    <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">MemDelete</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">):</span>  <span class="c1"># 회원삭제</span>
        <span class="n">textDlg</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">TextEntryDialog</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kc">None</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s1">&#39;삭제할 번호를 입력하시오&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s1">&#39;알림&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>  <span class="c1"># 입력창 띄우기</span>
        <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">textDlg</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">ShowModal</span><span class="p">()</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">ID_OK</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">textDlg</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">GetValue</span><span class="p">()</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="s1">&#39;&#39;</span><span class="p">:</span>
                <span class="k">return</span>
            
            <span class="n">delno</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">textDlg</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">GetValue</span><span class="p">()</span>
            <span class="n">data</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SelectData</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">delno</span><span class="p">)</span>
            <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">data</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="kc">None</span><span class="p">:</span>
                <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">MessageBox</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">delno</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="s2">&quot;번은 등록된자료가 아닙니다&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s1">&#39;알림&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">OK</span><span class="p">)</span>
                <span class="k">return</span>
            
            <span class="c1"># 삭제 작업 계속 진행</span>
            <span class="k">try</span><span class="p">:</span>
                <span class="n">conn</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">MySQLdb</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">connect</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">**</span><span class="n">config</span><span class="p">)</span>
                <span class="n">cursor</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">conn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">cursor</span><span class="p">()</span>
                <span class="n">sql</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s2">&quot;delete from pymem where bun=</span><span class="si">{}</span><span class="s2">&quot;</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">format</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">delno</span><span class="p">)</span>
                <span class="n">cursor</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">execute</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">sql</span><span class="p">)</span>
                <span class="n">conn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">commit</span><span class="p">()</span>
                <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">ShowData</span><span class="p">()</span>
                
            
            <span class="k">except</span> <span class="ne">Exception</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="n">e</span><span class="p">:</span>
                <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">MessageBox</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;삭제 에러 : &quot;</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">e</span><span class="p">),</span> <span class="s1">&#39;알림&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">OK</span><span class="p">)</span>
            
        <span class="k">else</span><span class="p">:</span>  <span class="c1"># 취소 눌렀을 때 </span>
            <span class="k">return</span>
        <span class="n">textDlg</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Destroy</span><span class="p">()</span>  <span class="c1"># TextEntryDialog 닫기 마무리 처리함</span>
    
    <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">SelectData</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">no</span><span class="p">):</span>  <span class="c1"># 레코드 읽는 메소드</span>
        <span class="k">try</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="n">conn</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">MySQLdb</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">connect</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">**</span><span class="n">config</span><span class="p">)</span>
            <span class="n">cursor</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">conn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">cursor</span><span class="p">()</span>
            
            <span class="n">sql</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s2">&quot;select * from pymem where bun=</span><span class="si">{0}</span><span class="s2">&quot;</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">format</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">no</span><span class="p">)</span>
            <span class="n">cursor</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">execute</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">sql</span><span class="p">)</span>
            <span class="n">data</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">cursor</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">fetchone</span><span class="p">()</span>
            <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">data</span>
            
        <span class="k">except</span> <span class="ne">Exception</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="n">e</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">MessageBox</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;추가오류 :&#39;</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">e</span><span class="p">),</span> <span class="s1">&#39;에러&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">OK</span><span class="p">)</span>
            
        <span class="k">finally</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="n">cursor</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">close</span><span class="p">()</span>
            <span class="n">conn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">close</span><span class="p">()</span>
                           
<span class="k">if</span> <span class="vm">__name__</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="s1">&#39;__main__&#39;</span><span class="p">:</span>
    <span class="n">app</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">wx</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">App</span><span class="p">()</span>
    <span class="n">MyFrame</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kc">None</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Show</span><span class="p">()</span>
    <span class="n">app</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">MainLoop</span><span class="p">()</span>
    
    
</pre></div>
